#######################################
## Sceanrio: L_DD_I2C_0011_0004
## Author: Mariia Nagul
## Date 31 Jan 2012
## Testing: Read/write a block phoenix addressable registers available in
## slave id 0x48-0x4a multiple times in burst mode.
#######################################

# Begin L_DD_I2C_0011_0004

01 set -x; i2cdump -f -y 0x1 0x48

02 set -x; i2cset -f -y 1 0x48 0x2 0x3

03 set -x; ii2cdump -f -y 0x1 0x4B

04 set -x; i2cdump -f -y 0x1 0x4a

05 set -x; i2cset -f -y 1 0x4a 0x2 0x3

06 set -x; i2cdump -f -y 0x1 0x4a

# End L_DD_I2C_0011_0004